  <brief_title>Randomised Study Comparing Different Dosages of Rabbit ATG in Patients With SAA</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Multicenter Study Comparing Different Dosages of Rabbit Antithymocyte Globulin (Thymoglobuline) in Patients With Severe Aplastic Anemia</official_title>
